\title{On the Nature of Trapped-Hole States in CdS Nanocrystals and the Mechanism of their }


\author{R. Peyton Cline, James K. Utterback, Steven E. Strong, Gordana Dukovic, and\\
Joel D. Eaves*\\
Department of Chemistry and Biochemistry, University of Colorado Boulder, Boulder,\\
Colorado 80309-0215, USA\\
